title: Penn State vs. Ohio State live stream: TV, time, channel, how to watch online
text:
Comments 
Ohio State will get a prime-time dress rehearsal before next week's game at Rutgers . The top-ranked Buckeyes look to remain perfect against Penn State on Saturday at 8 p.m. 
Next week, Rutgers will host the Buckeyes for an 8 p.m. kickoff at High Point Solutions Stadium. Penn State rolled over Rutgers, 28-3, in a primetime matchup on Sept. 19. 
While Ohio State is 6-0 and Penn State is 5-1, oddsmakers aren't expecting a close game. The Buckeyes are favored by 18.5 points. 
Here's everything you need to know about Saturday night's matchup: 
When: Saturday, Oct. 17 at 8 p.m. 
Where: Ohio Stadium, Columbus, Ohio 
TV: ABC...Chris Fowler and Kirk Herbstreit will call the game, with Heather Cox working the sidelines
